title: About
text:
Hello, I’m Zhe - an electrical engineer by trade and now working as a Senior Data Scientist at Snap Inc. working on recommender systems. My interests are in machine learning, statistics, signal processing and econometrics.
My goal with this site to is to write about the things I learn and find interesting.
